title: Sidewall, 1930–40
dimensions: Overall (b): 168 x 49.3 cm (5 ft. 6 1/8 in. x 19 7/16 in.)
creditline: Gift of Mark Bitter, Robert Bitter, Ward Bitter, and Tami Bitter Cook
description: Kitchen paper, featuring shelf-like plateaus with red plaid table cloth, with a shelf holding a coffee pot, cup and plate, alternating with a shelf holding two compotes. Separating each vertical row is a gray ribbon tied with blue plaid bow. Printed in colors on white ground.
